<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="privacypolicy.css">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- NavBar Partial -->
    <% include('partials/navbar') %>

        <div class="container">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>At <%= companyName %>, your privacy is important to us.
                    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information
                    when you interact with our website, purchase our online courses, or use our services.
                    Whether you're browsing our course catalog, enrolling in a course,
                    or simply staying up-to-date with our offerings, we are committed
                    to ensuring that your privacy is respected and your data is handled securely.

                    By using our website or purchasing any of our courses,
                    you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
                    Please take a moment to review the details below to understand
                    how we handle your personal information and your rights in relation to it.</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect various types of information when you visit our website or purchase courses from us,
                including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <% collectedInfo.forEach(info=> { %>
                    <li><strong>
                            <%= info.title %>:
                        </strong>
                        <%= info.description %>
                    </li>
                    <% }); %>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We may use your information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <% usageInfo.forEach(info=> { %>
                    <li>
                        <%= info %>
                    </li>
                    <% }); %>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p>We will not sell your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
            <ul>
                <% sharingInfo.forEach(info=> { %>
                    <li>
                        <%= info %>
                    </li>
                    <% }); %>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <% userRights.forEach(right=> { %>
                    <li>
                        <%= right %>
                    </li>
                    <% }); %>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or
                disclosure.
                However, no internet transmission is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your
                data.
            </p>

            <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. The
                updated
                version will be posted on our website with the effective date.</p>

            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>Email: <%= contactInfo.email %>
            </p>
            <p>Address: <%= contactInfo.address %>
            </p>
            <p>Phone Number: <%= contactInfo.phone %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Partial -->
        <% include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>